Happy Sunday! God is so good. I wanted to share my life shifting and very emotional experience i had at church earlier this year with you all. I was in LA visiting my best-friend and she wanted to bring me to her church with her before my flight. We never could’ve imagined what was going to take place when we got there. This was my first time going to One Chruch and is one of the most unforgettable moments of my entire life. To also share this moment with my best-friend and see her looking back at me just made it all the more special. He really works in mysterious ways. I couldn’t help but to just let go and let God! All the emotions came flowing out and I am forever changed from that moment on. Never forget God loves you, I love you and you aren’t going through the storm alone. Amen 🙏🏽

Behind the Scenes for the album cover shoot of ✨My Oasis✨ by @camrynlevert. Cam dropped this magical album 4 months ago 💖 (listen now on all streaming services!!!) We shot this back in March. We had a time 🥂 
.
Lotus, I learned so much from you in such a short amount of time and I’m honored to have worked alongside you. Thank you for being a wonderful soul and allowing me in your beautiful creative space 🫂🤍 
.
Goldie, your gift(s) is unmatched! You truly bring the ethereal aesthetic to life 🪄 Thank you for allowing us to create magic with your outta this world ideas 🤩 
.
Alexis, you weren’t with us physically, but your infectious beautiful spirit is always felt! You always enhance Cam’s beauty & you went tf off on this look (& every look you ever do) 😍💄
.
Camryn MFKN Levert! 💐 you have brought & continue to bring so much light in my life! To experience you in this phase of your journey is a blessing. You work so damn hard & show up authentically! For this to be your first album, I just…. Wow! Flabbergasted! Chef’s Kiss! All of that and more! I love you. I am eternally grateful for you. 💖
.
I have so much love & gratitude for God, my Angels + Ancestors! I prayed & continue to pray for opportunities & tribe that aligns with me and they always show me that I’m deserving to receive just that. All I can do is keep walking in my purpose with faith & be guided by them. 🤲🏼🤍
.
Songs: “Oasis” & “Treat Me Right” by Camryn Levert
